definitions.definition: A village in Claydon with Clattercote parish, Cherwell district, Oxfordshire , England ( OS grid ref SP4550 ) .
A village and civil parish (served by Claydon and Whitton Parish Council) in Mid Suffolk district, Suffolk , England ( OS grid ref TM1350 ) .
An unincorporated community in Rural Municipality of Frontier No. 19 , Saskatchewan , Canada .
